attachments.text: A community-driven effort to make web accessibility easier.

text: <!channel>: In case you missed it in general, The Diversity Committee is starting up a new food series! Similar to COOKIES, we will be hosting an event titled “Food: Celebration of Diversity” in which 4-5 people bring dishes (Costco samples style) to share with their coworkers. Each dish should in some way represent the person who brought it and, ideally, that person would be willing to share why! It can be a really great way to get to know and celebrate each others differences and upbringing while also enjoying delicious food! You can find a sign up form for the first ever Food: Celebration of Diversity right here <https://docs.google.com/a/uncorkedstudios.com/document/d/1IaXPC7l6ju4dBdZyjTtvJwA_kr17FnxCBBv1Yp7RIds/edit?usp=sharing> (one name per row please). Our flagship event will happen on Wednesday September 14th at 2pm.
<@U051P3FPY|kaitlyn> shared a file: <https://uncorked.slack.com/files/kaitlyn/F21UCG5HC/foodcelebrationofdiversity|FOOD: Celebration of Diversity>
